To enable ssh
https://www.simplified.guide/opensuse/enable-ssh
1 su
2 systemctl status sshd
3 systemctl start sshd
4 systemctl status sshd
5 systemctl enable sshd
6 firewall-cmd --permanent --add-service=ssh
7 firewall-cmd --reload
NOW SSH IS ENABLED

